text: Very peaceful morning at the beaches.. and sunrise is beautiful.

Family of chicken with the chicks are seen digging their claws into the soil in search of food. This park is teeming with lives as flora and fauna flourish among the vegetation rendering the environment full of vibes and energy.

Lush and beautifully landscape therapeutic garden with well paved paths for strollers. There is a standalone toilet within the garden and also a nice stone/pebble-filled dry stream with a garden pavilion next to it.
